## Quick Start

1. Run in development mode:
   ```bash
   kdeps run workflow.yaml --dev
   ```

2. Test the API:
   ```bash
   curl -X POST http://localhost:{{ port }}/api/v1/chat \
     -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
     -d '{"q": "Hello!"}'
   ```

